<!DOCTYPE codename-engine-dialogue>
<dialogue box="dialogueBox">
    <!-- Characters -->
    <char name="megablade" char="megablade" position="left" defaultAnim="look"/>
    <char name="pico" char="pico" position="right" defaultAnim="annoyed"/>
	<char name="pico-left" char="pico-left" position="left" defaultAnim="annoyed"/>
    <char name="bf" char="bf" position="right" defaultAnim="smile"/>
    <char name="grace" char="grace" position="left" defaultAnim="happy"/>

    <!-- Lines -->
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="look" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/1" changeMusic="dio/music/train" musicVolume="0.8" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        After what felt like an endless night, both Pico and Benjamin awoke feeling quite the opposite of well-rested.
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="smile" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/2" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        They left the “house of horrors”, which was actually quite pleasant during the daytime.
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="closedsmile" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/3" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        On foot, they spent the morning heading across town to the local train station.
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="closedtalk" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/4" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        In order to stay out of trouble, they planned to get as far away from the Fairests as possible.
    </line>
    <line char="pico-left" changeDefAnim="annoyed" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/5" changeMusic="dio/music/station" musicVolume="0.8" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Where’s the damn train?!
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="smile" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/6" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Calm down, it’ll be here soon, I’m sure.
    </line>
    <line char="pico-left" changeDefAnim="bored" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/7" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        It better come quick, we’ve already been set back enough.
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="nervous" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/8" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Yeah, I know.
    </line>
    <line char="grace" changeDefAnim="happy" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/9" changeMusic="dio/music/train-of-thought" musicVolume="0.6" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Benny!
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="slightsurprise" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        ?!
    </line>
    <line char="grace" changeDefAnim="happy" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/10" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        I haven’t seen you in weeks!
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="nervoussmile" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/11" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Heeeeeeeeeeeey Grace...
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="sweating" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/12" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        What’re you doing here...?
    </line>
    <line char="grace" changeDefAnim="smile" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/13" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Oh, you know, just out and about.
    </line>
    <line char="grace" changeDefAnim="thinklook" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        ...
    </line>
    <line char="grace" changeDefAnim="thinktalk" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/14" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Heeeeeeey, you know what would be fun? A duet! Just like old times!
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="sweating" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/15" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Uh, I’m sorry, I-I have to catch a train...
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="nervoussmile" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        It’ll show up before we’re done...
    </line>
    <line char="grace" changeDefAnim="look" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/17" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        I promise it’ll be quick!
    </line>
    <line char="grace" changeDefAnim="lookstar" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/18" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        And you know how I feel about promises!
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="concerned" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        ...
    </line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="nervoussmile" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/19" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Okay.
    </line>
    <line char="pico" changeDefAnim="annoyed" playSound="dio/sounds/playdate/20" nextSound="dio/sounds/advance">
        Son of a-
    </line>
</dialogue>